{"tid":469342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國醫院逼護士模仿女團跳淫舞","createTime":"2017-11-15T08:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T10:46:08.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"355fd8225964a158156c7e26b67dce354cb0ff4a","tid":469342,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T08:10:05.000Z","msg":"記者程思瑋／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n南韓知名的聖心醫院遭爆料，逼迫菜鳥護理師在年度運動會上大跳艷舞，還提供清涼舞衣讓他們穿，當著上千名賓客面前賣弄性感，無理要求讓護理人員覺得受辱，向上級反應卻被說小題大做，影片流出後，被痛批根本不尊重專業，把護理師當什麼？<br />\n<br />\n中空裝配上性感熱褲，一群辣妹大跳K-POP，炒熱現場氣氛，扭腰擺臀讓台下觀眾看得目不轉睛。南韓翰林大學聖心醫院一年一度的運動會，白衣天使助陣勁歌熱舞，但奇怪的是他們臉上都看不出喜悅。<br />\n<br />\n醫院相關人士：「要確定出席人數時，基本上大家都只能保持沉默，然後全員出席。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/11/14/1136319-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F1136319-XXL.jpg&h=e5c165b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲醫院逼迫懷孕護理師參加熱舞表演。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<br />\n原來台上舞者幾乎都是醫院菜鳥護理師，<span style=\"color: red;\">被「強迫中獎」參加表演，其中還有人甚至已經懷孕30周</span>，部分護理師當場跳到哭出來，加上本來分內的護理工作就已超量，還要加班練舞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/11/14/1136320-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F1136320-XXL.jpg&h=c5a233ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲護理師甚至被要求表演時張腿躺地。（圖／翻攝自TVCHOSUN）<br />\n<br />\n但類似事件還被爆不是第一次，他們曾在所謂安慰病人的活動上，被要求張腿躺地表演，讓人不知道到底用意何在，韓國護理人員協會要求全面調查。<br />\n<br />\n衛保處官員：「報告表示，一些文化的東西必須改變，它還強調尊重護理人員，和工作人員的人權文化。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/11/14/1136321-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F1136321-XXL.jpg&h=5e077f82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲院方回應，避免類似事件再發生。（圖／翻攝自TVCHOSUN）<br />\n<br />\n無視護理人員專業，被逼上演清涼秀，醫院基金會發言人表示，對「跳艷舞」事件不知情，院方也只回應，會避免類似事件再發生。（整理：實習編輯楊蕙瑜）<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=315049\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D315049&d=ywWURTQq08Fzn72WMUz%2FuY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=8c81e9c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D315049&h=e42b6e54\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=315049</a>"},{"pid":"1530cc86ec88f0f2843d9844a4b2bd80a0f650b0","tid":469342,"uid":75969,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T08:10:39.000Z","msg":"知你地想睇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BOo4GnCfoEo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBOo4GnCfoEo&d=ywWURTQq08Fzn72WMUz%2FuY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=aa85853e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BOo4GnCfoEo</a>"},{"pid":"0c727408a66b463e3de30654125f39e3530fdf88","tid":469342,"uid":49228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T08:12:23.000Z","msg":"kpop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8042e6d88a2de667fa70d3f4c83e019684296e4","tid":469342,"uid":139815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T08:12:53.000Z","msg":"幾多年前?<br />\n仲跳少女時代,4MINUTE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26f869806e9b6c9cb5cad0f7623ba7011cc437e9","tid":469342,"uid":608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T08:16:35.000Z","msg":"大肚都要跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48eca1275228f59a1f5ad19b2bc1e0173eb20482","tid":469342,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T08:22:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ee33ac4c7c1dd15167bfc560e2c3bc5d370625","tid":469342,"uid":103317,"like":0,"di